photos.caption: A male Vermilion Flycatcher on a bare branch, brilliant scarlet contrasting with dark gray wings.
A Great Kiskadee bursting out of a swimming pool in an explosion of water droplets after a plunge-dive.
A Crested Oropendola foraging among traveler's palm stalks, striking blue eye and pale bill visible against blue sky.
A Crested Oropendola perched on a banana, pale ivory bill and piercing blue eye against a clean blue sky.
A Rufous-tailed Hummingbird hovers with wings spread while feeding from cascading purple Petrea flowers.
A Scarlet-fronted Parakeet clinging to a mossy tree trunk, red forehead and bright green plumage visible.
A male Blue-necked Tanager showcasing its brilliant blue head and neck contrasting with turquoise shoulders and dark body.
A Common Squirrel-Cuckoo with rich rufous plumage and yellow bill perched on a lichen-covered branch.
A Bronze-winged Parrot clinging to a fruiting branch, showing dark scaly plumage and pink eye-ring.
A Bronze-winged Parrot feeding on fruit while hanging from a branch, pink orbital ring visible.
A Bronze-winged Parrot perched high against blue sky, dark plumage offset by red undertail coverts.
A Colombian Chachalaca walking along a metal railing with rufous-brown head and long rufous-tipped tail.
An Andean Motmot perched on a wire displaying its brilliant turquoise crown, red eye, and long racket-tipped tail.
A Roadside Hawk stares directly at the camera, yellow eyes and barred rufous breast in an alert perched pose.
A Spot-breasted Woodpecker atop a weathered stump displaying spotted breast and olive-barred back.
A pair of Spot-breasted Woodpeckers on bare branches with a misty mountain valley backdrop.
A Streak-headed Woodcreeper clinging vertically to a smooth palm trunk with streaked breast clearly visible.
An Yellow-backed Oriole perched on a bare branch, vivid orange crown and yellow-and-black plumage striking against green.
A Steely-vented Hummingbird hummingbird resting on a lichen-spotted branch, glittering green plumage catching the light.
A Steely-vented Hummingbird hummingbird resting on a dried leaf, dark iridescent plumage gleaming.
A Golden-faced Tyrannulet perched alertly on a leaf, showing pale underparts and olive-gray upperparts.
A Bare-faced Ibis perched on a lichen-covered branch, dark plumage showing iridescent green-blue wing sheen and bare pinkish face.
A pair of Spectacled Parrotlets investigating a hollow tree stump, blue eye-ring visible.
A Spectacled Parrotlet hanging upside down from a tree snag, peering curiously toward the camera.
A Bay-headed Tanager displaying its rich chestnut head, green back, and turquoise blue underparts.
A Bay-headed Tanager in profile showing the full spectrum from rufous crown through green mantle to blue rump.
An Acorn Woodpecker on a lichen-covered branch showing its distinctive clown-like face, red crown, and pale eye.
A Rusty-margined Flycatcher perched among berries, bold black-and-white head pattern and bright yellow underparts.
A male Long-billed Starthroat with bill open, displaying iridescent purple gorget and blue crown.
A male Long-billed Starthroat perched alertly, showing green-bronze back and violet throat.
A Guira Tanager glimpsed through branches, vivid orange breast partially obscured by foliage.
A Guira Tanager on a bare branch showing olive-gold upperparts with orange wing patches.
A Smooth-billed Ani perched atop leafy vegetation, all-black plumage with heavy ridged bill and long tail.
A male Lesser Goldfinch with bright yellow underparts and black cap perched on a branch among broad leaves.

A Yellow-bellied Seedeater perched among thorny branches, dark olive head contrasting with bright yellow belly.

A male Summer Tanager perched alertly on a branch, vivid red plumage glowing against lush tropical foliage.
